<section id="page-packer" class="page">
  <h1>C53 Packer</h1>
  <p>Mehrere CAMT.053 XML-Dateien auswaehlen und zu einer einzigen <code>.C53</code> Archivdatei (ZIP) zusammenpacken.</p>
  <div id="packer-drop-zone" class="upload-area" style="cursor:pointer">
    <p>XML-Dateien hier ablegen oder klicken zum Auswaehlen</p>
    <p class="upload-hint">Nur .xml Dateien, max. 50 Dateien, max. 5 MB je Datei</p>
    <input type="file" id="packer-file-input" accept=".xml" multiple style="display:none">
  </div>
  <div id="packer-file-list" style="margin-top:1rem"></div>
  <div style="margin-top:0.75rem;display:flex;gap:0.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
    <button id="packer-pack-btn" class="btn-primary" disabled>
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:0.25rem">
        <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
        <polyline points="3.27,6.96 12,12.01 20.73,6.96"/>
        <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/>
      </svg>
      C53 Archiv erstellen &amp; herunterladen
    </button>
    <button id="packer-clear-btn" disabled>Liste leeren</button>
  </div>
  <div id="packer-result" style="margin-top:1rem"></div>
</section>
